      • parseItemDetails

        public java.util.List<java.lang.String> parseItemDetails(WebLink webLink,
                                                         java.lang.String[] webPagePrasingKey,
                                                         java.lang.String[] productDescriptionPrasingKey)
                                                  throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
        Parse the saved web page to extract items' details specified in parsing key - one item per web page.

        Parsing process divided in five steps:
      • Step 1: extract cover url and all authors from web page -- webPagePrasingKey [0,3].
      • Step 2: find web page part with product details -- productDescriptionPrasingKey.
      • Step 3: extract publication year and publisher from publication details -- keys [4,5].
      • Step 4: extract ISBN from product details -- webPagePrasingKey [6,7].
      • Step 5: extract Average Customer Review from publication details -- webPagePrasingKey [8,9], e.g. 4.3 from "4.3 out of 5."

Parameters:
webLink - - contains the web page in String
webPagePrasingKey - - contains parsing keys to find item details
productDescriptionPrasingKey - - contains parsing key to find web page part with item product description
Returns:
List of Strings with item's details in order defined by parsing key, returns one item per method call
Throws:
java.io.FileNotFoundException - parsing failure due to inaccessible web page file
